"32:9:11" : {s: 32, a: 9, w: 11, r: "فاد", t: "وَٱلْأَفْـِٔدَةَ", l: "فُؤَاد", lc: 16, tl: "wal-afidata", lb: "অন্তর, হৃদয়, মন",e: "and feelings", b: "হৃদয়", f: 4, rm: "to hurt in the heart, be affected with heart disease, be struck in the heart. Motion, putting in motion When said of fuel; It burned, burned up, burned brightly or fiercely, blazed, or flamed: and so when said of the heart; It became excited with ardour, or eagerness. Heart, mind/intellect, sharpness/acuteness of mind."},
